preheader.content: Some useful information to get you started

html.content:
To view this email in your browser please click here
Welcome to Shell Fleet Solutions

Thank you for joining the Shell community, we’re glad that you’ve joined us.

Managing your fleet is made easier thanks to the tools we’ve got for you to take advantage of, including our online fleet management solution & our communications about your account, service updates, industry news, and our new products and services. 
Below is some useful account information in case you need to contact our Customer Service Centre. Please keep this safe.
Account Number
%%Legal_Entity_Account_Number%%

Account Contact 
UK-Account-Manager@shell.com
Shell Fleet Hub
If you’re eligible for Shell Fleet Hub, our online fleet management solution, we’ll send a registration email. From there, we’ll be in touch. Shell Fleet Hub makes running your fleet more efficient and more secure.

Click on the image below to find out  more. 
What comes next?
Here’s a sneak-peak of what to expect from Shell over the coming weeks:
Your Shell fuel cards will arrive in the next 5-7 working days
You and your fleet can then start using the cards at over 1,100 sites nationwide
You can also start to plan routes, download maps and find Shell sites nearby with our online Station locator
Here to help
We’ve created a webpage with some useful information and frequently asked questions to help guide you through your first few weeks with us. Alternatively, you can speak to our dedicated customer team on 0844 736 9617 or send us an email at generalcardrequests-uk@shell.com
Shell Fleet Solutions |
Privacy Policy |
Terms and Conditions

preheader.content: Heres how Shell can support you and your business

html.content:
To view this email in your browser please click here
         Your journey with Shell continues

We hope you’re settling in as part of the Shell community. Remember that our Customer Service Centre is available to support with any questions relating to your Shell account.

You can contact them on 0800 731 31 31.
Account Number
%%Legal_Entity_Account_Number%%

Account Contact 
UK-Account-Manager@shell.com
Shell Station Locator
Ready to get started? Use the Shell Station Locator to find a Shell station for your journeys. 
Step 1
Please visit the online Shell Station Locator to see our full network accessibility
Step 2
Simply type place names or postcodes into the search box. You can even add filters to narrow results down to those you need
Step 3
You will be provided with a list of service stations
 
Shell Station Locator

 


 
What makes us different?

Shell is committed to making a difference to the world we live in. Click the points below to find out more.
 
              
             
Whether you're just starting to consider alternative fuels or already have electric vehicles, your fleet will produce emissions that are just unavoidable. That's where our carbon offsetting service can help.
 		              
Find out more

 
              
             
Making transport cleaner: From electric to hydrogen cards, and developing biofuels, Shell is making transport cleaner.  		              
 
Find out more

 
              
             
We support sustainability: Shell is working on a variety of solutions to make the future of energy more sustainable - why not ask your account manager about our Shell Telematics solution. See how you could increase fuel economy by up to 20%* and/or monitor the performance of your electric vehicles with EV-specific reporting including EV driving energy consumption**
 		              
 
Find out more

 

*Source: Gartner, Market Guide for Transportation Mobility Technology, 2017
**Compatible with most electric and hybrid vehicles depending on age and model
 

 
                    

Here for you and your fleet

Want to hear more about using benefits of using your Shell cards?


Click below to hear a testimonial from one of our satisfied customers.
 
Here to help
We’ve created a webpage with some useful information and frequently asked questions to help guide you through your first few weeks with us. Alternatively, you can speak to our dedicated customer team on 0800 731 31 31 or send us an email at generalcardrequests-uk@shell.com
Shell Fleet Solutions |
